item.title: CVE-2019-4427|2024-09-16T17:39:13.204Z -- ibm -- cloud%20cli
item.description: IBM Cloud CLI 0.6.0 through 0.16.1 windows installers are signed using SHA1 certificate. An attacker might be able to exploit the weak algorithm to generate a installer with malicious software inside. IBM X-Force ID: 162773.
